## Compile

Use the termial version (CLI):

> Warning! You must have C++ 17!

```bash
make DEBUG=off
./output
```

Debug:

```bash
make
make run
```

To use the GUI version (in dev), you must have a Java sdk installed:

```bash
make runGui
```
